text: Orville Elliott (born 15 September 1885, date of death unknown) was a Canadian gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1885 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Canadian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Toronto
